description:
**Projections of Exposed People** provides insights into current and future population exposure to coastal flooding, combining population and flood projections to guide risk assessments and adaptation planning.​

​- **Sources**: Population projections from IIASA and GHS-POP, combined with CoCliCo flood maps.​
- **Common usage**: Supports exposure assessments and adaptation planning at all scales, informs risk management, engages stakeholders with accessible data, and helps prioritize investments and land-use decisions.​

More Info about the dataset: [User Handbook](https://www.openearth.nl/coclico-workbench/Datasets/#__tabbed_3_2)
